expectedTableValue.description:
Quarterly LIBOR Loan Rollover - New Rate (if applicable)

Loan currently has a floor of 0.71% - If 3 month LIBOR is above 0.71% we will require the rate.  

3 Month LIBOR - No Interp.  Interest Paid Monthly so new task to be set up in 3 months time  (Quarterly - July , October , January, April)

Programme Team to apply rate in Mambu.

RATE FIXING NOTICE:-
  1. Send BD/Customer Rate Fixing Notice and ensure rate confirmation is attached to account and rate notice is attached.  
  2. Ensure projected interest is correct in schedule following rate change (since rate change is only reflected in the system the next day).  If not, rate fixing notice to be completed next day to ensure interest in schedule is correct. 
  3. Ensure task is set up for next rate fixing date   (Quarterly - July , October , January, April)
